Changes Since 1.2.0

Breaking Changes

- IRssFeedBuilder.BuildFeeds now returns IAsyncEnumerable<SyndicationFeedResult?> (nullable items). Callers should handle possible null results.
- IRssFeedProcessor method signatures changed:
  - IsValidFeedModel(IRssFeedSourceBase? feedModel) (was IRssFeedBase?).
  - PreProcess(IRssFeedSourceBase? feedModel) (was IRssFeedBase?).
  - PostProcess(IRssFeedBase? feedModel, object? syndicationModel) unchanged.
- IRssFeedItemProcessor.ManipulateEnumerable now operates on IEnumerable<IRssFeedSourceItem?> (was IEnumerable<IRssFeedItem?>).
- IRssFeedStorageProvider method signatures changed to be language/host aware:
  - Task Save(SyndicationFeed? feed, string? internalId = null, string? language = null, string? hostName = null).
  - Task<Stream?> GetSavedStream(string id, string? language, string? hostName).
  Existing consumers must pass the appropriate language and host name when saving/retrieving. Stored blob paths now include hostName/language/id.xml.
- Model/interface changes introducing new “source” abstractions:
  - New: IRssFeedSourceBase, IRssFeedSourceContainer, IRssFeedSourceItem.
  - IRssFeedBase now extends IRssFeedSourceBase.
  Processors are expected to convert source instances to concrete IRssFeedContainer/IRssFeedItem as part of pre-processing.

Added Features

- Multi-language and host-aware feeds:
  - Feed discovery runs per enabled language and per site host.
  - FeedDiscoveryResult now includes Language and HostNameIdentifier.
  - SyndicationFeedResult now includes Language and HostNameIdentifier.
- Refactored Optimizely feed discovery to use IPageCriteriaQueryable, ILanguageBranchRepository and ISiteDefinitionResolver, with published-date sorting and per-feed item limits.
- Azure Blob storage provider saves and retrieves under hostName/language/id.xml for clearer separation across sites/languages.
- RssFeedBuilder improvements:
  - Computes feed LastUpdatedTime from items when available.
  - Adds logging and null-safety if pre-processing does not yield expected IRssFeedContainer/IRssFeedItem implementations.
- New internal helper IContentRssFeed to carry underlying IContent during processing.

Other Changes

- Multi-targeting and language version:
  - Target frameworks set to net8.0;net10.0.
  - C# language version updated to 14.
- Package and build updates (highlights):
  - GitVersion.MsBuild → 6.5.0.
  - Added: Azure.Identity, Microsoft.Data.SqlClient, SixLabors.ImageSharp, System.IO.Packaging.
- Repository metadata updated to GitHub URL in Directory.Build.props.
- Minor CI and documentation updates.

